    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 13th level, you can perform the following additional tasks with your @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Utk1OQRwYkMkFRD3]{Mage Hand} spell:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You can attempt to trip one creature within 5 feet of the hand. The creature must make a Dexterity saving throw against your spell save DC or be knocked prone.</li>\n<li>You can attempt to blind a creature within 5 feet of the hand. The creature must make a Constitution saving throw against your spell save DC or be blinded until the start of your next turn.</li>\n<li>You can deliver the effects of the @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.udsLtG0BugXHR2JQ]{Prestidigitation} spell originating from the hand.</li>\n</ul>",
